headline.print_headline: Warrant: Minnesota Doctor Saw Prince, Prescribed Drugs

docs.lead_paragraph: A Minnesota doctor saw Prince twice in the month before his death — including the day before he died — and prescribed him medication, according to contents of a search warrant that were revealed Tuesday as authorities returned to the musician's suburban Minneapolis estate as part of their investigation into what killed him.
